item.title: Sea Fish Recognition API
item.description: Sea Fish recognition API: Model developed with a RESNET 34 architecture with FastaAI2, Pytorch and Streamlite. The accuracy of the model in training was 7%. For the training of the model 44,134 images were used, which were scraped from the Internet.
